## Criteria Ownership Policy

Evaluation criteria are **user-controlled only**. No automated process may create, modify, or regenerate criteria. The ONLY valid paths to criteria changes are:

1. `PUT /prompts/criteria` — user edits directly via API/UI
2. `POST /prompts/criteria/generate` — user explicitly requests LLM generation via API/UI
3. `ensure_prompt_has_criteria()` — auto-generates ONLY on first discovery when no criteria exist at all

The feedback processor, periodic reviews, and prompt improvement tasks MUST NOT touch criteria under any circumstances. Criteria are the user's scoring contract with the judge. Automated feedback flows into the **agent description** (dynamic domain knowledge), not criteria.

